Class SystemStore<K,V>

java.lang.Object
  voldemort.client.SystemStore<K,V>
Type Parameters:
K - Type of Key
V - Type of Value
public class SystemStore<K,V>
extends java.lang.Object

A client interface for interacting with System stores (managed by the cluster). The naming convention is kept consistent with SocketStore (which is also a client interface).

Author:
csoman

SystemStore

public SystemStore(java.lang.String storeName,
                   java.lang.String[] bootstrapUrls,
                   int clientZoneID)
Wrapper for the actual SystemStore constructor. Used when we dont have custom Cluster XML, failure detector or a base Voldemort Client config to be used with this system store client.

Parameters:
storeName - Name of the system store
bootstrapUrls - Bootstrap URLs used to connect to
clientZoneID - Primary zone ID for this system store client (determines routing strategy)

Wrapper for the actual SystemStore constructor. Used when we dont have custom Cluster XML or failure detector to be used with this system store client.

Parameters:
storeName - Name of the system store
bootstrapUrls - Bootstrap URLs used to connect to
clientZoneID - Primary zone ID for this system store client (determines routing strategy)
baseConfig - Base Voldemort Client config which specifies properties for this system store client

SystemStore

public SystemStore(java.lang.String storeName,
                   java.lang.String[] bootstrapUrls,
                   int clientZoneID,
                   java.lang.String clusterXml,
                   FailureDetector fd)
SystemStore Constructor wrapper for the actual constructor. Used when we dont want to specify a base Voldemort Client Config.

Parameters:
storeName - Name of the system store
bootstrapUrls - Bootstrap URLs used to connect to
clientZoneID - Primary zone ID for this system store client (determines routing strategy)
clusterXml - Custom ClusterXml to be used for this system store client
fd - Failure Detector to be used with this system store client

SystemStore Constructor that creates a system store client which can be used to interact with the system stores managed by the cluster

Parameters:
storeName - Name of the system store
bootstrapUrls - Bootstrap URLs used to connect to
clientZoneID - Primary zone ID for this system store client (determines routing strategy)
clusterXml - Custom ClusterXml to be used for this system store client
fd - Failure Detector to be used with this system store client
baseConfig - Base Voldemort Client config which specifies properties for this system store client
